is a lot of meditation to make up.<br><br>Could a 47 Warrior solo one of these?  a 47 Rogue?  a 47 Cleric?  Maybe but unlikely or with much higher risk.  It has 4000ish HP and hits for 70 - 125 + Kick, maybe Double Attack.<br><br>There is so much variation in the Power of mobs that CON the same it is pointless to use that as a viable gauge.  A mob with enhanced move speed, that can cast, that can heal, that is immune to Stun or a particular damage type - these are far more deadly than a simple CON would reveal.  Con tells you if the Mob has a specified 'level' higher or lower than you.<br><br>Frankly, increased MOB AI and deadliness actually DETRACTS from the game, not enhances it.  Why?  VOLUME.<br><br>This game is designed so that to advance, you have to kill HUNDREDS and HUNDREDS of monsters.  If everyone of those fights had a significant chance of death, AND that death significantly set you back (as it does now), advancement would be nullified.<br><br>If you want a game with deadly AI, then you need to make a new game from the Ground Up.  This game is predicated on the fact that PCs will kill a LOT LOT LOT more Mobs than mobs will kill them.<br><br>Becasuse, quite honestly, if you on average, could only kill say 5 Mobs between deaths, you wouldn't advance very far. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/utwotribes.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Twotribes</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Board Troll</span><br>  Posts: 413<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(6/8/02 4:33:55 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2110.topic&inde